title: Stephanie Mills
itunes:title: Stephanie Mills
description:
Attention all a legend is in the house! This episode of Questlove Supreme is all about one of the most spectacular voices of our time, Stephanie Mills. She set the standard in her debut Broadway role as the original Dorothy in the Wiz and then came the hits.....Listen and learn about her life and everything in between only on Questlove Supreme!
